summary: An ordinance providing for the construction of a watermain on East Marginal Way, from Michigan Street, in the City of Seattle, to a point on the line between Section 3 and Section 10 in Township 23 North, Range 3 East, W.M., in King County, and other streets, appropriating money therefor, ratifying obligations and expenditures heretofore incurred under Ordinance No. 66167 and repealing said Ordinance No. 66167.
